script = ExtResource("3_sequence")
pages = Array[String](["Thanks for helping take care of those banshees, I was just taking a break in here, but im afraid the problem isn't solved. NO I'm not a vampire and this is not my fault, can't you see the mirror? Those banshees were corrupted by a bishop who lives nearby. We need to stop him to fully free the village, otherwise more banshees will keep coming and we'll have to keep purifying them."])

